 the issues that will be voted on during the annual meeting including decisions such as electing directors ratifying the selection of auditors and other shareholderrelated decisions including shareholderinitiated initiatives also proxies must disclose specific detailed information regarding the pay practices for certain executives       privacy policy terms of use about us contact us  salarycom all rights reserved us salaries canadian salaries purchase a salary report salaries by category salaries by income salaries by industry popular salaries negotiation tips benefits calculator search job openings job openings by state job openings by category education by career education by level education by major cost of living calculator john schiller obituary  houston tx  houston chronicle obituaries powered bysearch services geo h lewis  sons funeral directors  bering drive houston tx    website view map send flowers for more information about john schiller view funeral home obituary funeral homephoto gallery view photos resources more obituaries for john schiller looking for an obituary for a different person with this name john daniel jd schiller obituary condolences schillerjohn daniel jd schiller of houston texas departed this life unexpectedly on monday the th february  at  years of age jd was born in fort bend county on the nd of october  to father johnny joe schiller and mother liddie mae bravenec schiller who have both preceded him in deathas a young man jd collected a number of stock show ribbons his favorite registered jersey which he won in the  houston fat stock show was daisy whom he often talked about fondly in  jd graduated from missouri city high school and continued his education at texas am university he married his high school sweet heart jane broughton on the st of december  after graduating in  with an accounting degree and an aggie ring he proudly wore he began his career immediately with humble oil and refining and remained with exxon for  successful yearsjd was an active member of the community and constantly gave his time volunteering he filled his free time traveling and seeing new things watching aggie football fishing and spending time with his  children  grandchildren and  great grandchild jd is loved by an abundant family including nieces nephews cousins and friends he is survived by his wife jane broughton schiller son john daniel schiller jr and wife kristi son mark schiller and daughter karen schiller shepherd and husband troy his sister pat schiller bono and husband ben survive him as well his grandchildren also survive him john daniel schiller iii and wife veronica hailey schiller vickery and husband carl nicole shepherd susan shepherd brittain schiller sinclair schiller and a great granddaughter liddie vickery friends are cordially invited to a visitation with the family from five oclock in the afternoon until eight oclock in the evening on thursday the rd of march in the jasek chapel of geo h lewis  sons  bering drive in houstonthe funeral service is to be conducted at halfpast ten oclock in the morning on friday the th of march also in the jasek chapel of geo h lewis  sons where rev martin kaufman pastor of pilgrim lutheran church of houston is to officiatehonored to serve as pallbearers during the services are daniel schiller troy shepherd don broughton william broughton james vaccaro and scott dunwoodythe entombment is to follow via an escorted cortege at memorial oaks cemetery in houston where taps are to be sounded by a corps bugler from the texas a  m corps of cadets immediately following all are invited to a reception in remembrance of jd at a venue to be announced at the servicein lieu of customary remembrances contributions in mr jds memory may be directed to the pilgrim lutheran school  chimney rock rd houston tx  or to the salvation army  houston area command  austin st houston tx  published in houston chronicle from mar  to mar   read more remember share memories or express condolences